## Solution Overview

A full-featured Next.js 15 application leveraging React Server Components for direct Azure SDK integration, TypeScript, and shadcn/ui components. The application uses RSCs for all data fetching operations and Server Actions for mutations, eliminating the need for most API routes while maintaining security through server-side execution.

